              <span class="inline-block w-5 h-5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20.8 4.6a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.8 0L12 5.6l-1-1a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.8 7.8l1 1L12 21l7.8-7.6 1-1a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.8z"/></svg></span>
