              <span>Payments</span>
            </a>
            <a href="#security" class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/80">
              <span class="inline-block w-5 h-5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-3 8-10V6l-8-4-8 4v6c0 7 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></span>
